name: WFNU

Invocation Name: w. f. n. u.
des:
Listen to WFNU streaming radio on Alexa enabled devices. More information is available at www.wfnu.org.

To play the WFNU live stream, just say:
 -"Alexa, ask WFNU to play Live".

At anytime you can stop the radio by saying "Alexa, stop".

Other commands include 'Pause', 'Stop', 'Resume', 'Next' and 'Previous'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
